  <title>LAMMPS data files</title>

  <para>OVITO can write data files, which can be read the <link
  xlink:href="http://lammps.sandia.gov">LAMMPS molecular dynamics
  package</link>.</para>

  <para>If the atomic data to be exported contains velocity information it is
  written to the LAMMPS data file.</para>

  <para>If the output filename has a .gz suffix then the data file is
  compressed on the fly.</para>
</section>
